# Nagomi Seitaiin Website Walkthrough

I have created a professional, responsive top page for "Nagomi Seitaiin".

## Features
- **Design:** "Lifestyle Improvement" theme with a warm, professional Japanese aesthetic.
- **Responsiveness:** Fully responsive layout that adapts from mobile (hamburger menu) to desktop.
- **Technology:** Semantic HTML5 and modern CSS3 (Variables, BEM naming, Flexbox/Grid).

## File Structure
- [index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/nagomi-seitai/index.html): The main structure.
- [css/style.css](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/nagomi-seitai/css/style.css): All styling, using a clean architecture and variables for consistency.
- [js/script.js](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/nagomi-seitai/js/script.js): Minimal JS for the mobile menu toggle.
- `images/`: Generated assets (Hero image, Interior image).

